typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		pk_transaction_key as integer,
		net_binary_events_usd as decimal(28,10),
		dim_capital as string,
		dim_capital_branch as string,
		dim_business_area as string,
		net_ibnr_usd as decimal(28,10),
		dim_time_trans_date as date,
		net_ulae_usd as decimal(28,10),
		net_equalisation_reserve_usd as decimal(28,10),
		dim_time_incident_year as string,
		dim_time_financial_year as string,
		poolable_ind as string,
		hydra_ind as string,
		gross_equalisation_reserve_usd as decimal(28,10),
		gross_ibnr_usd as decimal(28,10),
		gross_ulae_usd as decimal(28,10),
		gross_binary_events_usd as decimal(28,10),
		text as string,
		source_system as string,
		date_inserted as timestamp,
		last_updated_by as string,
		inserted_by as string,
		date_last_updated as timestamp,
		dim_object_key as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from dwh_prepare.pre_fact_ibnr',
	format: 'query') ~> preFactIBNR
source(output(
		dim_capital_branch_key as string,
		amount_usd as decimal(28,10),
		dim_business_area_key as string,
		poolable_ind as string,
		hydra_ind as string,
		dim_time_incident_year_key as string,
		dim_time_financial_year_key as string,
		dim_time_trans_date_key as date,
		pk_pre_fact_man_rbns_adj as long,
		amount_net_usd as decimal(28,10)
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from dwh_prepare.pre_fact_man_rbns_adj',
	format: 'query') ~> preFactManAdjRBNS
